<section class="content-card editor-page reveal">
  <header class="editor-header">
    <div>
      <p class="editor-kicker">Local Draft Console</p>
      <h1>文章编辑器</h1>
      <p>用于起草 Hexo Markdown 文章，内容只保存在当前浏览器中。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="editor-actions">
      <button class="editor-button" type="button" data-editor-action="copy">复制 Markdown</button>
      <button class="editor-button editor-button-primary" type="button" data-editor-action="download">下载 .md</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="editor-shell">
    <form class="editor-form" autocomplete="off">
      <label>
        <span>标题</span>
        <input id="draftTitle" type="text" value="新的学习笔记">
      </label>
      <label>
        <span>Slug / 文件名</span>
        <input id="draftSlug" type="text" value="new-learning-note">
      </label>
      <label>
        <span>分类</span>
        <input id="draftCategories" type="text" value="Reading Notes, Digital Design">
      </label>
      <label>
        <span>标签</span>
        <input id="draftTags" type="text" value="digital-design, risc-v">
      </label>
      <label class="editor-wide">
        <span>摘要</span>
        <textarea id="draftExcerpt" rows="3">这是一篇新的学习笔记摘要，用于首页和文章列表展示。</textarea>
      </label>
      <label class="editor-wide">
        <span>正文 Markdown</span>
        <textarea id="draftBody" rows="18">## 问题背景

这里记录学习动机、章节来源和核心问题。

## 硬件结构

- 信号流：
- 时序关系：
- 边界条件：

```verilog
module example (
  input  wire clk,
  input  wire rst_n
);
endmodule
```

## 复盘

这里整理仿真结果、波形观察和后续问题。</textarea>
      </label>
    </form>

    <aside class="editor-output">
      <div class="editor-output-header">
        <span>Markdown 输出</span>
        <strong id="draftFilename">new-learning-note.md</strong>
      </div>
      <textarea id="draftMarkdown" rows="13" readonly></textarea>
      <div class="editor-output-header">
        <span>预览</span>
        <strong id="draftStatus">已同步</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="editor-preview post-content" id="draftPreview"></div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
